### Get all vehicles
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/vehicles/

### Create a vehicle
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/vehicles/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "registration_number": "GJ01AB1234",
  "vehicle_name": "Van-05",
  "vehicle_type": "Van",
  "max_load_capacity": 500,
  "acquisition_cost": 800000
}

### Get single vehicle (ID = 1)
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/vehicles/1

### Update vehicle (ID = 1)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/vehicles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "In Shop",
  "odometer": 1500
}

### Delete vehicle (ID = 1)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/vehicles/1

### Create a driver
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/drivers/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex Kumar",
  "license_number": "DL123456789",
  "license_category": "LMV",
  "license_expiry_date": "2027-05-20",
  "contact_number": "9876543210"
}

### Get all drivers
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/drivers/